		"description": "<ul>\n<li>Your Intelligence score increases by 1.</li>\n<li>Whenever a scholar ability would require you to spend inspiration, you may instead expend a hit die.</li>\n<li>You gain the @UUID[Compendium.a5e-bloody-heretics.bloody-heretics.Item.DhH2HdUvPQYNIbWE]{Accelerated Recovery} ability, and add your scholar and bloodblade levels together to determine the CR of creatures you can affect. &nbsp;If you would already have the Accelerated Recovery ability, you may instead regain hit dice equal to either your constitution or intelligence modifier, whichever is higher.</li>\n<li>The duration of your mark from the @UUID[Compendium.a5e-bloody-heretics.bloody-heretics.Item.as2ADovft2mxBCWa]{Scholar of the Blood} feat is also increased to 1 hour.</li>\n</ul>",
